<h4><a name="_RefGameOptions">Game Options</a></h4>
<p>The Game Options tab is located on the lower portion of the game setup screen.  This tab contains
options and information that are common to all players.  Only the captain has the ability to modify
these options.</p>

<p><b>** Place Game Specific Game Options information here **.</b></p>

<p><a href="#_RefTop">Return to Top</a></p>

<h4><a name="_RefPlayerOptions">Player Options</a></h4>
<p>The <i>Player Options</i> tab is located on the lower portion of the game  setup screen.  This
tab contains options that are specific to each player.  Each player may only modify his or her own
options.</p>

<p><b>** Place Game Specific Player Options information here **.</b></p>

